description: This skill allows Alexa to give you a randomly-generated quote from a U.S. President. Just say "Alexa, launch Presidential Quotes" to get started.
exampleInteractions: "Alexa, ask presidential quotes to give me a quote."
"Alexa, ask presidential quotes to tell me a presidential quote."
"Alexa, ask presidential quotes to give me a presidential quote."
name: Presidential Quotes
